description:
鏵智房地產營銷策劃(香港)有限公司
華發實業(香港)有限公司全資下屬公司
珠海華發集團旗下房產板塊
房地產開發商自己的銷售團隊

工作職責 : 

l   負責銷售大灣區住宅樓盤;

l   處理客戶查詢及售後服務;

l   與客戶建立及維持良好長期關係;

l   協助組織銷售活動及日常銷售工作。


要求:

l   大專程度以上;

l   具有房地產或銷售經驗者優先考慮；

l   熟悉基本電腦操作;

l   能操流利廣東話、普通話;

l   具良好溝通技巧, 有責任感, 積極主動。

Responsible for promoting IT Solutions and AI products to Public Utility and or Education sector;
Degree or diploma holder with at least 5 years’ sales experience in I.T. & AI solutions;
Able to develop opportunities within assigned account territory and explore new accounts;
Solid track records in account development and management especially in Public Utility and or Education sector
Self motivated and able to lead a small team in conducting sales and business development activities;
Proficiency in both spoken and written English and Chinese (Mandarin and Cantonese) with strong presentation skill is a must. 
Please send your full detailed resume with expected salary and date available to The Human Resources Manager, NEC Hong Kong Limited, 25th Floor, The Metropolis Tower, 10 Metropolis Drive, Hunghom, Kowloon or by e-mail.



Personal data provided by job applicant will be used strictly in accordance with employer's personal data policy, a copy of which will be provided immediately upon request.

中五或以上
流利廣東話
負責日常銷售工作及產品推廣
具有銷售經驗者優先考慮
經驗較少者可被考慮為初級門市銷售員
提供在職培訓，無經驗者亦會考慮
上班時間（需輪班）：
星期一至星期六：10:00 a.m. - 8:00 p.m.
星期日及銀行假期：1:00 p.m. - 7:00 p.m.



Benefits:    

Year-end performance bonus; 
Medical plan (Worldwide);
Birthday leave;
Exam leave;
Funeral leave;
Paternity leave;
MPF scheme;
Training & Development plan;
Staff purchase company product discounts.
